eling.', 'Synergism', 'The risk of hepatic injury should be considered when brentuximab vedotin is used with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/296176/', '', 'Fludrocortisone, Fluocinolone acetonide, Hydrocortisone, Prednisolone, Betamethasone, Fluorometholone, Methylprednisolone, Dexamethasone, Salicylic acid, Fluocinolone acetonide, Cortisone, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Amivantamab, Atezolizumab, Pembrolizumab, More', 1767369485);
